OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfwat complacent over      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FThames Water affair - MP   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ofwat has been accused of being        
OL,6, "complacent" over the Thames Water     
OL,7, affair, which has seen it lose its     
OL,8, chief executive and face collapse over 
OL,9, its massive debts.                     
OL,11,FThe company is fighting for survival   
OL,12,Fand has until early next year to stave 
OL,13,Foff temporary nationalisation.         
OL,15,FMP Sir Robert Goodwill said the        
OL,16,Fregulator had questions to answer over 
OL,17,Fwhether it had "been asleep at the     
OL,18,Fwheel" over the case.                  
OL,20,FOfwat faces MPs on Wednesday.          
